==English==

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A [[mound]] of [[earth]].
# A [[rounded]] [[fleshy]] [[mass]], such as on a [[camel]].
# A [[deformity]] in [[human]]s caused by [[abnormal]] [[curvature]] of the [[upper]] [[spine]].
#{{slang}} An act of [[sexual intercourse]].
#{{slang}} (''British'') A [[bad]] [[mood]], especially in the expression ''to [[have the hump]]''.
#{{slang}} A [[painful]]ly [[boorish]] person.
#:''That guy is such a hump!''
# ('''The Hump''') World War 2 slang for the [[supply]] route between India nnd China over the Himalaya mountain range.

